### List all available groups
GET http://localhost:3001/schedule/groups

### List all lecturers
GET http://localhost:3001/schedule/lecturers

### Full schedule (all sections)
GET http://localhost:3001/schedule

### Schedule for a specific group (replace with actual group id from /groups)
GET http://localhost:3001/schedule/group/31_2

### Schedule for string group (II stopien)
GET http://localhost:3001/schedule/group/CY1

### Schedule for lecturer by abbreviation
GET http://localhost:3001/schedule/lecturer/JW.
